      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 997.2 Carrera S, showcasing the peak of Porsche\u2019s naturally aspirated, rear-engine engineering. This example features the 3.8L 9A1 power plant with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), eliminating the IMS bearing concerns of predecessors. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. The vehicle is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), featuring a 10mm lower ride height and recalibrated damping rates for superior lateral grip. Every mechanical component is in superlative condition; the cooling system, high-pressure fuel pumps, and coil packs have been preemptively serviced. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key, concours-level machine for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
